rows.label: qst105607_msg0001
rows.name:
Wow. I've never been in this room
before. All right, so where are we at?

rows.label: qst105607_msg0002
rows.name:
If I were a book in this dusty old
place, where would I hide?

rows.label: qst105607_msg0003
rows.name:
Aha! ...No, wait, it's just an old legal
tome.

rows.label: qst105607_msg0004
rows.name:
D'awww! It's a portrait of ickle
Zeke! You were such a darling
little Prince!

rows.label: qst105607_msg0005
rows.name:
Whoa, whoa, hold on, what are you
looking at?! Put that back!

rows.label: qst105607_msg0007
rows.name:
I can't seem to find anything like
what we're after...

rows.label: qst105607_msg0008
rows.name:
Hmm. His Majesty isn't the type to lie
about this sort of thing...

rows.label: qst105607_msg0009
rows.name:
Yeah, deffo. Just like how he wouldn't
lie about being the direct descendant
of Adel.

rows.label: qst105607_msg0011
rows.name:
Just pulling your leg, Saika. Anyway,
we've turned up nothing. Looks like
we'll have to tell Dad we can't find it.
